snippet.title: Pac-Mazing (Pac-Mania arcade game clone) (by Luca Carminati, LC-Games)
snippet.description:
Download Pac-Mazing from https://lowcarb.itch.io

This game is a homage to Pac-Mania developed by Namco in 1987.

Main differences from the original version:

- Randomly generated mazes

- Bonus rounds

Author: Luca Carminati (lucacarminati1967@gmail.com)

Read the "Instructions.txt" file for more info.
